text: Nargis Fakhri (born 20 October 1979) is an American model and actress who acts in Indian movies. She has appeared on America's Next Top Model. Fakhri started her acting career in the 2011 Bollywood movie Rockstar. She went on to star in the Bollywood movies Madras Cafe (2013), Main Tera Hero (2014), and had a supporting role in the Hollywood movie Spy (2015). == References == Category:Actors from Queens Category:1979 births Category:Living people
